                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "Software architecture is the foundation upon which all code is built. Without a clear architectural vision, projects inevitably devolve into tangled dependency graphs.\n\nClean Architecture offers a disciplined approach to organizing code that keeps business logic at the center while pushing infrastructure concerns to the edges.\n\n## The Dependency Rule\n\nThe fundamental rule is simple: source code dependencies must point inward.",
